[h3 id=Stage1TheForest 
	" Stage 1, The Forest
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Collect 6 pieces of paper to exit the stage. Jumping and running are equally fast, but jumping avoids the skeleton attacks. There is a teleporting mage who shoots magic missiles, but we have enough health that no frames are lost to dodging any attacks.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Stage2ThePalace 
	" Stage 2, The Palace
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"The guards are a deadlier version of the skeletons, but jumping avoids their sword strikes. The pink rhinos that shoot fireballs can do lots of damage but Spartacus has just enough health that no frames are lost to dodging.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"After the princess is rescued she follows Spartacus while the guards try to kill her. Spartacus moves fast so the princess follows him offscreen and the guards can never attack her. The last jump can end input early by a few frames.
	$LF
]div
